{"tid":2103442,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"銀保監會指未來潛在風險仍大 有影子銀行死灰復燃","createTime":"2020-07-11T08:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T08:01:54.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"42b69c98290c88d63a587f23b2b73c38dc67aa69","tid":2103442,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T08:01:54.000Z","msg":"銀保監會指未來潛在風險仍大 有影子銀行死灰復燃<br />\n2020-07-11 HKT 15:42<br />\n<br />\n&quot;(中國)銀保監會發言人說目前有幾方面風險；第一是不良資產上升壓力增加；第二是有銀行、保險或信託公司，存在大股東操縱及內部人士控制的情況，管治機制失效，資產品質在疫情衝擊下加速變差，風險不斷積累。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;另外，一些高風險影子銀行死灰復燃，部分更以新形式或新面目，企圖捲土重來，有資金違規流入房市及股市，推高資產泡沫。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537167-20200711.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537167-20200711.htm&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=50e422b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537167-20200711.htm&h=4696cdf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537167-20200711.htm</a>"}]}